name: Feed Ur Babbies 4: Down the Hatch
name_original: Feed Ur Babbies 4: Down the Hatch
description:
Controls: up and down arrow to move, space bar to fly

This year I learned that nuthatches line the entrance of their nest holes with sticky pine resin to keep out pests and predators. The nuthatches avoid this by flying directly into the opening without touching the sides.

Made for 0 Hour Game Jam between the hours of 2am and 2am

You can watch me build this game here: https://www.twitch.tv/videos/788537541
